Find Your Perfect Home at Banyan Bay Apartments in Jacksonville

See Floor Plans

Welcome to Banyan Bay Apartments, your oasis of luxury living in the heart of Jacksonville. Nestled on the serene San Pablo Road, just a stone's throw away from the bustling Atlantic Boulevard, our resort-style apartments offer the perfect balance of convenience and serenity. With Atlantic Beach and Neptune Beach just a short drive away, our pet-friendly community offers a perfect blend of convenience and coastal charm. What truly sets us apart is our unwavering commitment to exceptional customer service and multitude of resort-style amenities that transforms everyday living into a never-ending vacation. Banyan Bay is located in the most sought-after school district in Jacksonville near the area’s best schools!

Banyan Bay Floor Plans & Availability

Banyan Bay offers four different style floor plans ranging from one to four bedrooms. Our relaxing homes are thoughtfully designed featuring gourmet-style kitchens with separate dining areas and roomy bedrooms boasting ample closet space. Each apartment home offers modern stainless-steel appliances and includes full-size washer and dryer appliances for your convenience. To elevate your living experience, you also have the option to select apartments with soaring nine-foot ceilings, a cozy fireplace, or picturesque lake views, making your dream home a reality.

Close to Jacksonville’s Best Dining, Shopping, and Entertainment

When you choose Banyan Bay, you’ll love the quick and convenient access to some of the area’s major attractions like St. Johns Town Center, the University of North Florida, TPC Sawgrass, Mayo Clinic and so much more! Love the beach? You'll be happy to know that Banyan Bay is located just minutes away from breathtaking beaches including Atlantic Beach, Neptune Beach, and Jacksonville Beach.

Enjoy Local Discounts with Our VIP Program

At Banyan Bay Apartments, we’re committed to adding value to your living experience, which is why we’re excited to offer our Resident VIP Program! As a Banyan Bay resident, you’ll enjoy exclusive discounts and special deals at a selection of Jacksonville’s best local businesses. Craving a delicious meal? Enjoy resident-only perks at popular spots like V Pizza and Bono’s Pit Bar-B-Q. If fitness is your focus, take advantage of discounts at Baileys Health & Fitness to keep your wellness routine on track. Need a coffee pick-me-up? Ellianos Coffee offers residents a special perk to make mornings even better. Our VIP Program is all about connecting you to the community while adding convenience to your lifestyle. It’s our way of saying thank you for being part of Banyan Bay Apartments. Enjoy these exclusive benefits and make the most of everything Jacksonville has to offer!
